The paper proposes a deep learning model for recommender systems, which involves learning feature interactions. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers topics related to deep learning and recommender systems. The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, which are covered by cs.IR and cs.AI respectively. The paper uses real-world datasets, which suggests that it may also belong to the data science (cs.DS) and database (cs.DB) categories.
